    <title>Preface</title>

    <para>I wrote this book in the way a cookbook is written. Each recipe
    works for itself. Each topic contains of a lot of code examples.</para>

    <para>If you are an absolute beginner than you must start reading the very
    first chapter (<xref linkend="ruby-grundlagen"/>). There is absolute no
    way to understand Ruby on Rails without understanding the basics of Ruby.
    I made that mistake a couple of years ago, so trust me.</para>

